title: Ep - 100 - KRISTEN DOUTE FROM VANDERPUMP RULES
description:
Kristen Doute from Vanderpump Rules talks about how she was cast for the show, whether she has a game plan after the show ends, how she feels responsible for DJ James Kennedy having a spot in the cast, her new friendship with Arianna, and how the entire cast is able to drink so much and stay skinny. 


Kate makes her older sister Megan take a reality show description quiz and surprisingly doesn’t fail it. 


Kate’s dad Paul reviews an episode of the UK show Made in Chelsea.
